      • convertTestFiles

        public void convertTestFiles​(TestRepresentation testRepresentation,
                             java.lang.String outputDirectory)
        Converts a given TestRepresentation to jUnit test files.
        Firstly, converts the TestRepresentation to a JunitTestClasses and maps them to TestClasses. Delegates the creation of the directory to the FileDirectoryCreator.
        Delegates the creation of the test files to the TestFileCreator.
        Prints a success message, if the test files have been created successfully.
        Specified by:
        convertTestFiles in interface TestConverter
        Parameters:
        testRepresentation - the TestRepresentation describing the structure of the tests to be created.
        outputDirectory - the file path where the directory of the tests files has to be created.
